			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Iron Fertilization Isn’t Going to Save Us</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">The controversial geoengineering technique can defer, at best, a few years’ worth of emissions. And that’s ignoring the potential side effects.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/jack-mcgovan/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Jack McGovan</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						January 12, 2024 | 1,000 words, about 5 minutes					</aside>
