						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AIron Fertilization Isn’t Going to Save Us%0D%0AThe controversial geoengineering technique can defer, at best, a few years’ worth of emissions. And that’s ignoring the potential side effects.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/iron-fertilization-isnt-going-to-save-us/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



